**Elasticsearch version** (`bin/elasticsearch --version`):
7.10.0+
**Description of the problem including expected versus actual behavior**:

Foreach processor passes a special context to the internal processors. The `inference` processor seems to not support these fields internally. 

**Steps to reproduce**:

```
POST _ingest/pipeline/_simulate
{
  "pipeline": {
    "description": "detect text lang",
    "processors": [
      {
        "foreach": {
          "field": "greetings",
          "processor": {
            "inference": {
              "model_id": "lang_ident_model_1",
              "inference_config": {
                "classification": {
                  "num_top_classes": 5
                }
              },
              "field_map": {
                "_ingest._value.text": "text"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "foreach": {
          "field": "greetings",
          "processor": {
            "append": {
              "field": "foo",
              "value": ["{{_ingest._value.text}"]
            }
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "docs": [
    {
      "_source": {
        "name": "George",
        "greetings": [
          {
            "text": "Hello"
          },
          {
            "text": "שלום"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

